  - "how does Tesla make money"
  - "what's a good Italian restaurant in Toronto"
  - "how's the market"
  - "any news about Sam Altman"
  - "whats happening with crypto rn"

Diversity REQUIREMENT: every query in this batch must be substantively
different from every other query in this batch. Use varied named entities
(specific teams, companies, locations, products, people). Do NOT generate
multiple paraphrases of the same query.

Now output the JSON array of {{ count }} new examples. Output ONLY the array.
